  "logNo": "110127171668",
  "title": "아들에게서 받은 첫번째 크리스마스 카드",
  "addDate": "2011. 12. 23.",
  "categoryNo": "1",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110127171668",
  "html_size": 181449,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110127171668\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110127171668\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p>오늘 한의원으로 전해진 한통의 초록색 봉투.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>아들이 다니는 어린이집에서&nbsp;&nbsp;아빠에게 카드보내기 행사를 한다는 소식을 들었었는데,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>드디어 올것이 왔구나 ^^</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20111223_122/isuhani_1324606670525yBTst_JPEG/%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA_%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA%C4%AB%B5%E5.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"410\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 410px\" id=\"20111223_122/isuhani_1324606670525yBTst_JPEG/%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA_%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA%C4%AB%B5%E5.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A4174854')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20111223_122/isuhani_1324606670525yBTst_JPEG/%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA_%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA%C4%AB%B5%E5.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>이것 저것 가리니까.. 누너기가 되버렸지만.. 음음.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>자식에게서 처음 받는 우편물은 이렇게 소중한거구나 싶더군요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>조심조심 개봉해서 내용물을 꺼내봅니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20111223_1/isuhani_1324606725241iyX64_JPEG/%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA_%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA%C4%AB%B5%E5_2.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20111223_1/isuhani_1324606725241iyX64_JPEG/%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA_%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA%C4%AB%B5%E5_2.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A4174854')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20111223_1/isuhani_1324606725241iyX64_JPEG/%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA_%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA%C4%AB%B5%E5_2.JPG?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>ㅎㅎㅎ</p>\r\n<p>산타 만들었네요</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(이거 만드느라 선생님은 얼마나 고생하셨을까... 싶기도 하고 ^^)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>카드를 펼쳐봅니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20111223_133/isuhani_13246069005327maQh_JPEG/%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA_%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA%C4%AB%B5%E5_3.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"410\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 410px\" id=\"20111223_133/isuhani_13246069005327maQh_JPEG/%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA_%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA%C4%AB%B5%E5_3.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A4174854')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20111223_133/isuhani_13246069005327maQh_JPEG/%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA_%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA%C4%AB%B5%E5_3.JPG?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>ㅎㅎㅎㅎㅎㅎㅎ</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>그냥.. 웃음만.. ㅎㅎㅎㅎㅎㅎ</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>아들이 크리스마스카드라고 만들면서 어떤생각을 했을까 궁금하기도 하고</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>이걸 아빠가 보고서 매우~! 기뻐할거라는 걸 알기는 할까 싶기도 하네요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>그리고 이걸 같이 만드느라(사실 거의 다 혼자서 하셨겠죠) 고생하셨을 선생님도 떠오르기도 하네요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>사랑한다~ 아들!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
